description: The Sony E-Series Walkman MP3 Player delivers up to 50 hours of music -with video and photo playback plus FM radio just to sweeten the deal. With delicious colors, Windows drag and drop functionality and digitally restorative Sony Clear Audio Technologies, the E-Series is bling to the ears and eyes.What's in the box: Sony 16GB E Series Walkman Video MP3 Player (Black),3 x Earbud Adapters (Small/Medium/Large),Earbud Headphones (MDR-EX083),Media Go Software (Preloaded),Walkman Software (Preloaded),User Software (Preloaded),USB Cable and 1-Year Limited Warranty.
title: Sony NWZE465 16 GB Walkman MP3 Video Player (Black) (Discontinued by Manufacturer)
